page.title: 03AN AUTOBIOGRAPHY
page.content: My name is CELIA FERRY ,I am twelve years old.I live at WIDDRINGTON it has a railway station. I have a sister who is two years old,she is called Antonia.My house is medium sized,it has three bedrooms, a kitchen,a living room, a dining room a bathroom and it has a loft.It also has a back and a front garden. I have relatives in Italy,I have been to see them.I have also been to Tunisia. We travel around on the bus but most of the time we go in our car, it is a dark green Viva. I have no pets,I used to have two Goldfish but they died. I also used to have two baby rabbits but we had to give them to my cousin. We called the rabbits Dempsey and Makepeace.
